ActCanadian Commercial Corporation Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister for International Trade of ROBERT H. KWON of Toronto, Ontario, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Commercial Corporation, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Andrew Saxon, whose term has expired.
